Class DirectoryDataLoader

public class DirectoryDataLoader
extends DataLoader

The basic directory data loader implementation. This one reads straight from .json files rather than from .blob stuff or whatever the hell compressed or encrypted data format is used for data entries.

Description copied from class: DataLoader
